title: Digital Puppet Masters Tournament Series - 1v1 - Starting Tommorrow 6pm

embed.description: This organization will run tournaments for teams and players of all ranks and skill level, with a main focus on League Of Legends in the Oceanic Region.

body:
The Digital Puppet Masters 1v1 series will be starting again tommorrow night Monday 29th January 2018.

Prizes are as follows;

63 participants or fewer:
1st Place: 750 RP
4-win XP boost for all participants

64 participants or more:
1st Place: 1000 RP
2nd Place: 500 RP
4-win XP boost for all participants

If you are interested in playing please register anytime and check-in to the battlefy client between 6-6.30pm AEDT on Monday and join the discord channel.

the link are as follows:
Battlefy :- https://battlefy.com/digital-puppet-masters

Discord :- https://discord.gg/4eqBU8X

regards Dungeon
